metadata.description: Mutant Alien Ape Yacht Club Mutant AlienApeYC is an NFT collection consisting of 10,000 Mutant AlienApeYC NFT on Ethereum blockchain ERC-721. This collection is mutated version of Alien Ape Yacht Club! The apes are stored as ERC-721 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain and hosted on IPFS. $AlienApeCoin will be launched soon. You will be able to stake AAYC and MAAYC NFT collection and Earn $AAPE Token.
